Important Information  Recruiting Fraud  





 Nabors has been extraordinarily successful for a long time because of unique products and services. But perhaps the most unique component of the company is our workforce. Comprised of approximately 95 nationalities, our skilled and talented employees enable Nabors to operate efficiently in more than 20 countries. They routinely set performance records, suggest new and better ways to conduct our operations and design and patent technology that is changing the way the oil and gas industry does business. Most important, they prove every day that a commitment to excellence is easily understood in any language. 


























